These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, aconite
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, dannemann, dunhill
House: colonial, palace, modern
1. the colonial house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person who growszinnia is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the colonial house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower         | orchid | zinnia   | aconite   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | bolivar    | dannemann      |
| House     | palace     | colonial      | modern |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, scientific, documentary
House: victorian, ranch-style, futuristic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, rose
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsrose##1
4. the person watching satire movies is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the ranch-style house and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific  | satire     | documentary     |
| House   | ranch-style     | futuristic     | victorian      |
| Flower   | rose  | daffodil | balloon-flower |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

