.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, coffee
3 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, roller, subway
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person drinking coffee and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person eating kale##1
5. the person driving the van is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Beverage           | coffee | sprite  | fanta   |
| Game   | domino  | whist    | mah-jongg |
| Transport           | subway     | van | roller |

