.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, sunflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, soul, disco
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, pink, ivory
1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the person who growssunflower is between the fan of soul and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person who growsaconite is the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Flower    | iris       | sunflower  | aconite   |
| Music-Genre     | soul    | disco  | d&b |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Color   | ivory | coral     | pink      |

