.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
City: marseilles, paris, edinburgh
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
House: palace, cottage, gothic-revival
3 different games are played: billiard, go, monopoly
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the person playing billiard is between the gothic-revival house and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person playing go##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City          | edinburgh    | marseilles     | paris      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| House   | gothic-revival  | cottage       | palace       |
| Game           | go     | billiard       | monopoly     |

