The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, handball
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, chaman, baccarat
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the accountant is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is between the architect and the chaman-smoker##2
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Job          | architect | journalist | accountant    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Sport   | skateboarding   | baseball     | handball        |
| Cigar           | aristoff      | baccarat       | chaman      |

