2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person eating pepper##2
5. the person eating cabbage is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Food      | grapes       | cabbage      | pepper      |
