The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, superhero, scientific
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, february, march
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, funk, disco
1. the fan of disco is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in march##2
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the fan of funk##1
6. the fan of funk is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Movie-Genre          | superhero   | drama      | scientific     |
| Birthday   | march  | november      | february |
| Music-Genre     | trance | disco        | funk     |

