.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, ferret
House: victorian, cottage, tower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, august, october
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the cottage house is between the victorian house and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is the tower house##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Pet       | rabbit       | ferret       | fish    |
| House         | tower | cottage | victorian |
| Birthday       | august      | october         | may |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

