The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, volleyball, swimming
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, trike
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
4. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Movie-Genre      | thriller     | action | romance      |
| Sport         | volleyball  | swimming       | water-polo |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Transport   | snowmobile | airplane    | trike     |

