There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, townhouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, amber, orange
1. the baccarat-smoker is between the person who likes amber and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person who likes amber##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Cigar      | pall-mall    | baccarat          | siglo |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| House           | ranch-style | townhouse | gothic-revival         |
| Color   | white    | orange    | amber      |

