.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, purple, amber
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, train
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, pilot
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the pilot##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the fisherman is between the person who likes pink and the person driving the airplane##2
4. the lawyer is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who likes purple and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Color      | pink | amber     | purple        |
| Transport         | bus   | train | airplane |
| Job   | lawyer        | fisherman       | pilot      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

