.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
House: art-deco, ranch-style, colonial
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, firefighter, electrician
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person playing billiard is the accountant##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the accountant##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the colonial house##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the electrician and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| House        | ranch-style      | art-deco | colonial |
| Game         | billiard     | scrabble    | bridge        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Job   | accountant          | firefighter     | electrician       |

 